  "description": "Noise-forward granular voice built from tiny grains — 0.08 size — with moderate posScatter 0.5 and pitchScatter 0.15. The result is breath: not noise, not pitch, the thing between. Low filter cutoff, medium resonance, fast attack. Play softly for whisper, hard for exhale. The body before it decides to sing.",
